result.formatted_address: 香港堅尼地城卑路乍街22號
result.name: 吾系茶記 Anka's Kitchen

reviews.text: 午飯經過這裡，看看放在門口的是日午餐牌，都有想吃的東西，便走進去。選擇了雞扒但不想吃飯，用豉油汁配意粉雖然有些奇怪，香港人甚麽都會試，便大胆地點了。喝完附送青紅蘿蔔湯，主菜便送到，雞扒不肥膩，肉質嫩滑，味道不重，沒有黑胡椒或其他重味道，個人比較喜歡這種雞扒，可想像到豉油意粉是甚麼味道，如果鼓油汁太少，可叫他們加添；這是不錯“輕午餐”。
價錢少許貴，但座位相對濶落，食品質素ok,值得推薦！
不似預期，價格同食物不合比例，
Reasonable price, tasty food without msg. Reminds me of my mom's cooking.
幾好，幾乾淨，適合我!而且味道還不錯!👍👌

reviews.text: Okay squid ball with dry noodles for a bit pricy price. The noodles were a little too salty. Limited seating but it doesn't get too busy. English menu upon request and staff understands English as well. Fast and really good service.
Very good and hot noodles. The fish dumpling 魚皮餃 is really authentic and good worth a try. Noodles arrive quick and takeout is available as well. Good prices for good food really enjoy!
Local Chiu chau style small noddle shop. Good taste.
Probably the best Chiu Chow noodle restaurant in K-town, their squid ball is super yummy, chili oil very good 2!!
It's a popular local shop selling fish balls, squid and pork balls, beef slices and other fish delicacies. A good place for tasty noodles at lunch or dinner. No frills tho.

result.formatted_address: 香港西環卑路乍街15G地下
result.name: 榮記潮州粉麵

reviews.text: 墨魚丸河同墨魚鬚💕💕
勁正墨魚丸，扺食夾大件，呢碗淨紫菜墨丸，$34，有下次！

唔敢講話 no. 1，但西環嚟講粉麵鋪可叫高質
墨魚鬚是必食

好有嚼口的墨魚丸

好耐冇到西環走走，今天就到堅尼地城新海旁 看看海景、吹吹海風。今天海旁的風很勁，真的很勁，但是有很多年靑的俊男美女在拍照，風中的美女，風中的俊男，大家都很享受。風實在太勁，我急急腳便離開，真的受不了。

沿著卑路乍街走，一間以前常光顧的粉麵店仍在，現在除了潮州粉麵外 還有粥品供應。我好喜歡他們的墨魚丸河，今天當然要懷舊一番。個粉端上時已有陣陣的蒜香味，湯很熱，河粉很滑，墨魚丸結實彈牙，真是佳品。

魚旦河也很不錯，魚旦是不規則狀，不是機械唧出來的，有魚味，彈牙爽口，除了真的是好吃也帶上幾分懷念之情。
平宜又味美的傳統廣東麵，湯底尤其好，味道好之餘無放太多味精。

reviews.text: Awesome food, every dish that we tasted was well-balanced and perfectly executed. Very popular with the locals and also a Michelin-star eatery, so expect a long queue.
Good place to satisfy your sweet tooth on a budget. Excellent service with good knowledge of products and nice display.

Excellent food and price was reasonable.  Tasted the deep fried fresh anchovies the first time.  The vegetables were very fresh.  This restaurant is busy all the time.  It is better to make reservation in advanced.
Packed with happy diners. High intensity. Massive menu. Be ready to eat!
It is a good place if you never taste taochew dishes, they are serving these dishes as the taste is the same with taochew.
